text: KF Vardari Forinë (, FK Vardar Forino) is a football club based in the village of Forinë, Gostivar Municipality, North Macedonia. They are currently competing in the Macedonian Second League (West Division). ==History== The club was founded in 1974. ==References== ==External links== *Vardari Forino Facebook *Club info at MacedonianFootball *Football Federation of Macedonia Vardari Forino Category:Association football clubs established in 1974 Category:1974 establishments in the Socialist Republic of Macedonia FK Vardari
